### Retailer Inventory Management API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Retailer's Inventory
GET {{baseUrl}}/retailers/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Inventory Stock and Reorder Level
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/retailers/inventory/update/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity_in_stock": 100,
  "reorder_level": 20
}

### Restock Inventory (Add Stock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/retailers/inventory/restock/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 50
}

### Get Low Stock Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/retailers/inventory/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Place Wholesale Order (Retailer buying from Wholesaler)
POST {{baseUrl}}/retailers/order/wholesale
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "product_id": 1,
      "quantity": 50,
      "seller_id": 2
    },
    {
      "product_id": 3,
      "quantity": 100,
      "seller_id": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Get Retailer's Purchase Orders (from wholesalers)
GET {{baseUrl}}/retailers/orders/purchases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Retailer's Sales (to customers)
GET {{baseUrl}}/retailers/orders/sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
